"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-07-olympics-star-smashes-european-record-immediately-proposes-partner-paris-21379517\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Alice Finot had a day to remember on Tuesday as she broke the European record in the 3000m steeplechase and then immediately proposed to her partner who was in the stands at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"score\": 0.9984946053839417, \"rank\": 0.0015076642457459773, \"text\": \"Alice\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_and_Bob\"}, {\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.115643502110137e-14, \"text\": \"European record\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\"}, {\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 16, \"to\": 21}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 44}, {\"ngram\": \"the 3000m steeplechase\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 103}, {\"ngram\": \"her partner\", \"from\": 137, \"to\": 148}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French star missed out on a medal as she finished fourth but it was an immense performance from her, setting a personal best and the fastest time ever by a European in the women's race.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 200, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.889425096847309, \"rank\": 0.11553292973758503, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"an immense performance\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest time\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"a European\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's race\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After celebrating on the track Finot headed over to the stands where her partner was waiting and Bruno Marti\\u0301nez Bargiela had the surprise of his life.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"her partner\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"Bruno Marti\\u0301nez Bargiela\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"the surprise\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finot got down on one knee and asked her boyfriend to marry her, presenting a pin rather than a ring and she explained why afterwards.\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one knee\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"her boyfriend\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"a pin\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 621}, {\"ngram\": \"a ring\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow all the action from Paris 2024 on our live Olympics blog.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999997492068, \"rank\": 2.5079945616847125e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the action\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"our live Olympics blog\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I told myself that if I ran under nine minutes, knowing that nine is my lucky number and that we have been together for nine years, then I would propose,' Finot said, having cross the line in eight minutes and 58.67seconds.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nine minutes\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"my lucky number\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"nine years\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"eight minutes\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"58.67seconds\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not like doing things like everyone else.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since he had not done it yet, I told myself that maybe it was up to me to do it.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I gave a pin that I ran with to my boyfriend.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pin\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"my boyfriend\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On it, it says: \\\"Love is in Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997025952, \"rank\": 2.974839862495121e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Love\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"se